---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="MX+C | Applied AI Product Engineering" description="We help ambitious teams design, ship, and scale practical AI products with clear delivery and measurable outcomes.">
  <section class="hero reveal">
    <p class="eyebrow">Applied AI Product Engineering</p>
    <h1>
      Serious software, <br />
      <span class="serif">not AI theatre.</span>
    </h1>
    <p>
      MX+C partners with founders and product teams who need working AI systems, not slide decks.
      We scope aggressively, build quickly, and stay accountable to outcomes.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="button primary" href="/about#contact">Book an intro call</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/docs">How we work</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="hero-stats">
      <li>
        <strong>Prototype first</strong>
        <span>Early validation before heavy build-out</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Weekly checkpoints</strong>
        <span>Transparent updates and explicit tradeoffs</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Production mindset</strong>
        <span>Maintainable systems from day one</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="logo-strip reveal delay-1" aria-label="Who we support">
    <p>Built for ambitious product teams in fintech, climate, insurance, and spatial data.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal delay-2">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h2>What we deliver</h2>
      <p>We focus on small, high-impact engagements that remove technical uncertainty quickly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid service-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>AI Product Prototyping</h3>
        <p>Define the thinnest useful product and ship it fast enough to learn from real users.</p>
        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li>Problem framing and success criteria</li>
          <li>Rapid UX and technical prototyping</li>
          <li>Go/no-go recommendation</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Model + Data Pipelines</h3>
        <p>Turn messy data and notebooks into repeatable, testable workflows.</p>
        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li>Data ingestion and quality checks</li>
          <li>Model training and evaluation loops</li>
          <li>Monitoring-ready outputs</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Production AI Features</h3>
        <p>Integrate inference and automation into your product with reliability and clear ownership.</p>
        <ul class="mini-list">
          <li>API and service integration</li>
          <li>Guardrails and fallback behavior</li>
          <li>Rollout and instrumentation</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal delay-3">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Delivery Model</p>
      <h2>How an engagement runs</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <article class="timeline-step">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Scope</h3>
        <p>We align on the outcome, constraints, and what “good” looks like.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="timeline-step">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Build</h3>
        <p>We deliver in short cycles with visible progress and decision logs.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="timeline-step">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Prove</h3>
        <p>We test against real data and user behavior, not happy-path demos.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="timeline-step">
        <span>04</span>
        <h3>Handover</h3>
        <p>You get a maintainable system plus clear next steps for scale.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section reveal delay-4">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Example Work</p>
      <h2>Typical project outcomes</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card case-card">
        <h3>Geo-imagery annotation assistant</h3>
        <p>
          Designed a workflow for prioritizing aerial imagery review and reducing manual annotation overhead.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card case-card">
        <h3>Decision-support prediction service</h3>
        <p>
          Built a reliable API-backed prediction feature with explicit uncertainty and clear operational controls.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-panel reveal delay-5">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Start here</p>
      <h2>Have a real problem to solve?</h2>
      <p>
        Send a short brief. If we can help, we will suggest a practical first sprint.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <a class="button primary" href="mailto:contact@mxpc.io">Email contact@mxpc.io</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/about#contact">See contact details</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
